Class BodyTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • skyproc.Record
      • skyproc.BodyTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BodyTemplate
extends Record
    A internal structure found in many major records representing body setups. The use depends on the context of the major record it is inside of.
